No. 11-6692. Kenneth D. Beverly, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1030, 132 S. Ct. 561,

181 L. Ed. 2d 416,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8004, November 7, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.
